          <div class="d-sm-flex justify-content-center justify-content-sm-between">
            <span class="text-muted d-block text-center text-sm-left d-sm-inline-block">Copyright Â© 2020-2021 <a href="bootstrapdash.com">BootstrapDash</a> and <a href="https://github.com/dotmattdev/regal-dashactyl">mattt#6969</a></span>
